===Pronunciation===
זאת / zô'th / zothe'

Irregular feminine of {{HH|2089}}; this (often used adverbially): - hereby (-in, -with), it, likewise, the one (other, same), she, so (much), such (deed), that, therefore, these, this (thing), thus.